next: PRODUCTIONIZE the Imbens-Manski CI (branch feature/analytic-ci). Bias investigation RESOLVED: NO material finite-sample bias (single-Psi ~unbiased; population bound contains truth; earlier "[1.06,1.07]" was one unlucky sample). Under-coverage is the IM narrow-set-vs-noise problem; IM CI (built in R/bound_ci.R) achieves nominal coverage at n=500 (NIE 0.12->0.93, NDE 0.09->0.95). Remaining: mediator primitive + bound_ci_mediator, wire ci_method="analytic" into bound_ne, full coverage table N{100,200,500} both paths OR/RR/RD, tests, CRAN. See PLAN-bias-investigation-2026-06-12.md.
